    {
      "instruction": "<p>Whilst the steak is resting, return the reserved pan to a medium heat with a drizzle of <strong>vegetable oil</strong></p><p>Once hot, add the <strong>sliced mushrooms</strong> and cook for 5-6 min or until softened and browned</p><p>Dissolve your<strong> chicken stock mix</strong> in 100ml <span class=\"text-purple\">[130ml]</span><span class=\"text-danger\"> [180ml]</span> <strong>boiled water</strong></p>",
      "order": 5,
      "media": {
