      "instruction": "<p>Once the mushrooms have browned, add your <strong>Chinese rice wine</strong> and cook for 1 min</p><p>Add your <strong>chicken stock</strong> and<strong> soft cheese</strong> and cook for 3-4 min further or until thickened</p>",
      "order": 6,
